data.value: # Instruction List # # Loading Values # "LOADI <R0> <V>" R0 = V # "MOV <R0> <R1>" R0 = R1 # # Register Register Math # "ADD <R0> <R1>" R0 = R0 + R1 # "SUB <R0> <R1>" R0 = R0 - R1 # "MUL <R0> <R1>" R0 = R0 * R1 # "DIV <R0> <R1>" R0 = R0 / R1 # "MOD <R0> <R1>" R0 = R0 % R1 # # Value Register Math # "ADDI <R0> <V>" R0 = R0 + V # "SUBI <R0> <V>" R0 = R0 - V # "MULI <R0> <V>" R0 = R0 * V # "DIVI <R0> <V>" R0 = R0 / V # "MODI <R0> <V>" R0 = R0 % V # # Jump # "JMP <L>" PC = addressof(L) # "JMPZ <L>" PC = addressof(L) if Zero Flag # "JMPNZ <L>" PC = addressof(L) if Not Zero Flag # "JMPN <L>" PC = addressof(L) if Underflow Flag # "JMPNN <L>" PC = addressof(L) if Not Underflow Flag # "JMPO <L>" PC = addressof(L) if Overflow Flag # "JMPNO <L>" PC = addressof(L) if Not Overflow Flag # # Controle # "RST" Restart # "HOLD" Stop # "EOF" End of file (RST + HOLD)
